<div class="alert alert-info mb-4" role="alert">
    <h4 class="alert-heading"><span class="bi bi-info-circle"></span> MVVM Messaging Sample</h4>
    <p>
        This page demonstrates loosely-coupled component communication using the <code>IMessenger</code> pattern from
        CommunityToolkit.Mvvm. Components send and receive messages without direct references to each other.
    </p>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h6><span class="bi bi-diagram-3"></span> Component Communication Flow</h6>
            <ul class="small">
                <li><strong>TextEntry Component:</strong> Sends <code>ConvertAsciiToHexMessage</code>, receives <code>ConvertHexToAsciiMessage</code></li>
                <li><strong>HexEntry Component:</strong> Sends <code>ConvertHexToAsciiMessage</code>, receives <code>ConvertAsciiToHexMessage</code></li>
                <li><strong>Parent ViewModel:</strong> Broadcasts <code>ResetHexAsciiInputsMessage</code> to all recipients</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h6><span class="bi bi-gear"></span> Features Demonstrated</h6>
            <ul class="small mb-0">
                <li><strong>RecipientViewModelBase:</strong> Base class for ViewModels that receive messages</li>
                <li><strong>IRecipient&lt;TMessage&gt;:</strong> Interface for handling specific message types</li>
                <li><strong>Messenger.Send():</strong> Broadcast messages to all registered recipients</li>
                <li><strong>Decoupled Communication:</strong> Components communicate without direct references</li>
                <li><strong>Type-Safe Messages:</strong> Record types ensure compile-time safety</li>
                <li><strong>Bi-directional Updates:</strong> Changes in one component update the other</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr />
    <p class="mb-0">
        <span class="bi bi-lightbulb"></span> <strong>Try It:</strong>
        Type text in either box and click the send button to see the conversion. The "Clear" button demonstrates
        broadcasting a message from the parent to multiple child components simultaneously.
    </p>
</div>
